=== Access ===
About 10 minutes by car from the Shiratoriouchi Interchange on the {{ill|lt=Takamatsu Expressway|Q7677132|qid=Q7677132|1=Takamatsu Expressway}}. Located along {{ill|lt=Kagawa Prefectural Route 129 Suinushi Sanbonmatsu Line|Q11667426|qid=Q11667426|lt=Kagawa Prefectural Route 129|1=Kagawa Prefectural Road Route 129}}.

